%h1 Stores
%p Stores is a solo project that I started recently. It's another Java based implementation, this time featuring an updater, saving and loading and throttling! What I mean by throttling is that it's focused to be a pacing game. Your first time playing will probably last about a minute or two but the idea is that, hopefully, you'll come back! 


