%h1 Project Ditch (Working Title)
%p Project Ditch is a Java text-based game. Kind of like a throw back to retro gaming.

%p It features a parsing engine that allows for natural (like regular human speech) text to be entered and parsed correctly.

%p Future plans include porting the game to mobile platforms such as iOS, Android and Blackberry

